  <h1> All About Driving </h1>

  <p>In order to win, you need to know what do do when your driving. The most essential thing you must know when playing this game is how to make the kart go and how to make it turn. Making the kart go and turn are pretty easy
    but there is somehing more difficult when it comes to turning. Thats learning how to drift. Its going to make a little while to get used to but in the end, it will
    seem like a piece of cake. Basically, you press the ZR button on the Wii U gamepad while using the control stick to drift in the direction you want. If you keep drifting, you'll eventually get blue sparks on your tires. If that goes on, you'll be able to get orange sparks. Heres a chart to help you understand the button inputs for Mario Kart 8.
