<h1>Secrets to Mastering this Game</h1>

<p> If you think you have what it takes to be a professional in this game, brace yourself. Like I said at the beginning, there is more than you think. The first thing we are going to talk about in
  is fire hopping. Fire hopping is just one of the techniques that any pro would know in this game. When you fire hop, you need to make sure that you have a orange spark when you drift for the big boost. When you get the boost, press the ZR button rapidly and when you do that, make sure you move the control stick from one side to the other quickly too.
  Hm? Why should you want to do this? Well, because not only will it make your boost faster, it will also last longer too. Its hard to pull off but with practice, anyone can get it. An example of fire hopping would be this...
